---
---

<section id="about" class="px-6 sm:px-10 py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

    <div class="fade-up">
      <span class="sec-tag">— About</span>
      <em class="block font-body italic text-xl text-cream/70 mb-3">the person behind</em>
      <h2
        class="font-display font-light text-fog leading-[0.92] mb-12 tracking-tight"
        style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.25rem);"
      >
        The Reader<br><span class="text-parchment">&amp; Builder</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="border border-dust p-7 flex flex-col gap-5">
        <div>
          <span class="font-galaxy text-[0.5rem] tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-ash block mb-2">currently reading</span>
          <p class="font-body italic text-base text-cream/75">The Hours — Michael Cunningham</p>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px bg-dust"></div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-galaxy text-[0.5rem] tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-ash block mb-2">currently building</span>
          <p class="font-body italic text-base text-cream/75">
            <em class="text-parchment not-italic">UnDrift</em> — a privacy-first distraction-aware AI
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px bg-dust"></div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-galaxy text-[0.5rem] tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-ash block mb-2">currently thinking about</span>
          <p class="font-body italic text-base text-cream/75">attention as a form of love. whether focus can be taught.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px bg-dust"></div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-galaxy text-[0.5rem] tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-ash block mb-2">now playing</span>
          <iframe
            style="border-radius:2px;border:none;display:block;"
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/1cPLddXCqw6uzyWy6tdtlK?utm_source=generator"
            width="100%" height="80"
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            loading="lazy">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fade-up" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
      <span class="sec-tag">— Introduction</span>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 font-body text-cream/70 leading-[1.9]"
           style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);">
        <p>
          I'm an undergrad at Plaksha University studying Computer Science &amp; Artificial Intelligence —
          but the truest version of that sentence is that I'm someone trying to make sense of the world
          through code, prose, and a dangerous number of books.
        </p>
        <p>
          Right now I'm building
          <a href="#projects" class="text-parchment underline underline-offset-2 decoration-parchment/25 hover:decoration-parchment/70 transition-all">UnDrift</a>
          — a real-time, privacy-first AI assistant that helps people stay present with what matters.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l border-dust pl-5 my-1">
          <p class="font-body italic text-ash/80 leading-[1.75]">
            "words do not express thoughts very well. they always become a little different
            immediately after they are expressed, a little distorted, a little foolish."
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          I love Virginia Woolf, Ayn Rand, Sylvia Plath. I love aerospace and astronomy and
          the particular feeling of encountering a black hole in a physics textbook at midnight.
          I'm wary of the internet — thanks, Snowden — and very much on it anyway.
        </p>
        <p>
          My fragments are scattered. That's the point. Explore the
          <a href="#projects" class="text-parchment underline underline-offset-2 decoration-parchment/25 hover:decoration-parchment/70 transition-all">work</a>,
          read the
          <a href="/blog" class="text-parchment underline underline-offset-2 decoration-parchment/25 hover:decoration-parchment/70 transition-all">writing</a>,
          or just wander.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<div class="marquee-strip" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="marquee-inner reverse">
    {[
      'builder','reader','researcher','writer','dreamer',
      'CS & AI','Plaksha University','India',
      'builder','reader','researcher','writer','dreamer',
      'CS & AI','Plaksha University','India',
    ].map(item => (
      <span class="marquee-item">{item}<span class="marquee-dot"></span></span>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>